Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:25.75,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:28.87,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,So many people and carriages!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:37.24,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... The Royal Academy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:42.02,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.22,0:00:46.21,main,Old Lady,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly started feeling ill...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:46.96,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:01:00.16,main,Old Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I feel better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:03.62,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad. You'll be all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:07.72,main,Daughter,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much. How can I ever repay you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.72,0:01:08.92,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:12.42,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,It took a long time since I'm only level 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:16.58,main,Daughter,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. Who knows what would have \Nhappened to my mother if not for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.24,0:01:19.30,main,Daughter,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, by any chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.13,0:01:22.95,main,Daughter,0000,0000,0000,,Were you on your way to the Royal Academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:25.56,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm moving into the dorm today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.79,0:01:28.05,main,Daughter,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then you'd better hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.05,0:01:28.77,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:32.07,main,Daughter,0000,0000,0000,,I believe the academy's \Ngates close at 6 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:33.29,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:47.85,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:53.46,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:55.90,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to lock the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:02:00.47,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,It's the rule that the Royal \NAcademy's main gate closes at 6 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:04.17,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,But the bell hasn't even finished ringing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.71,0:02:07.05,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,And now it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:09.25,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,Your name and grade?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.89,0:02:13.24,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Alicia Ehnleit. I'm a new first-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:16.38,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, the color of your necktie... \NAren't you a first-year, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:19.11,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I've been helping with the weekly duties
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.87,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,to get myself accustomed to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:25.19,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, the rules are absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:27.75,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to find lodging \Nin town for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:30.64,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,But the entrance ceremony is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.97,0:02:33.88,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get into the dorm today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:39.38,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, um... I don't have that much money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:44.83,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you're the one commoner \Nwho was admitted here this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:47.06,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I don't sympathize...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:52.15,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,But rules are rules. Just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:54.98,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,What?! But you're a first-year, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:56.59,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:03:00.77,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what I'm about to say \Nis just me talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:01.45,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:04.75,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,There's a part of the wall on the \Neastern side that's crumbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:08.77,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,Students who break curfew often \Nenter and leave through there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:11.37,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,You're unlikely to be seen at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:15.17,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:18.99,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I hadn't introduced \Nmyself yet. How rude of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:20.93,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Oswald Grimsarde.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:24.74,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Grimsarde? I've heard that \Nname somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:27.80,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,Probably my father. He's a \Ncabinet minister, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:29.68,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,You're the son of a minister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:34.21,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,My father is my father, and I am \Nme. Please call me by my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:37.46,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I'll call you Oz, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:38.84,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oz?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:46.56,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Oz! You're a nice guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:48.71,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we'll be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.16,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:04.09,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:06.23,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,You broke curfew too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:08.30,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you in. Give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:08.97,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.14,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:14.46,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go. Ready, and... up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.13,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,You're really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:21.50,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Just follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:25.20,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I'm William Ares. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:28.49,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Alicia Ehnleit. Are you \Na new first-year, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:33.46,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The older guys in the dorm \Nsent me to buy drinks for a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:34.49,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:36.65,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:42.32,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,It's sort of a ritual for \Nnew kids entering the dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:43.19,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.00,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your step there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:52.39,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. You really are strong, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:55.77,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's a general.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:58.22,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,He's been training me since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.45,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,A minister and a general...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.61,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,All the people here are from \Nsuch impressive families.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:07.32,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Don't space out. If you're \Nnot paying attentionâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:12.62,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,I-I... I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.07,main,Boys,0000,0000,0000,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:17.42,main,Boys,0000,0000,0000,,They just fell through the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.58,main,Boys,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:22.09,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,That... didn't hurt? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:24.43,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:26.41,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind getting off of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.60,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:32.10,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:34.79,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Alicia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:38.10,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ed. That had to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:40.01,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Ed? Are you two friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:44.24,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've known Will since we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:48.40,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Edwin Valschein,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:51.24,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,the second prince of the \NKingdom of Valschein.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:52.93,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,A prince?!
