Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:27.46,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't even had the \Nentrance ceremony yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:31.43,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,and you're already causing a commotion. \NYou don't waste time, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:35.39,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,As the principal, I feel that \Nmakes you worth teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:37.05,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,This is all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:38.47,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.87,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I got distracted 'cause you talked to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:41.79,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:43.19,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:46.60,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,William Ares...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:49.57,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be confiscating this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:54.92,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,And Alicia Ehnleit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:56.07,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:08:00.08,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,You have a rare and precious \Ntalent for light magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:05.87,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,That is why you were the one and only \Ncommoner admitted here on a scholarship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:10.09,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,Always be aware of that, and mind \Nyour behavior going forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:11.61,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:14.09,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,You will both be given extra duties \Nfor one week as punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:17.00,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,You are to work together, and no fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:18.33,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,You may go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.73,main,Alicia/William,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:30.48,italics,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's Alicia Ehnleit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:38.87,italics,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,She's our kingdom's last hope \Nof salvation from the Demon Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:47.76,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,I screwed up on my first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:51.69,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,I showed up late, broke a window, and \Neven got punished with extra duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:53.20,main,TeacherA,0000,0000,0000,,Intruder!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.55,main,TeacherB,0000,0000,0000,,There's an intruder! Capture him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:57.16,main,TeacherA,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:09:00.18,main,TeacherB,0000,0000,0000,,He may have climbed the wall to get outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:02.46,main,TeacherA,0000,0000,0000,,Go and look. I'll check the dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:03.31,main,TeacherB,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:06.71,main,TeacherA,0000,0000,0000,,There's been an intruder on school grounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:08.44,main,TeacherA,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, stay inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.43,main,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:10.80,main,GirlB,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.07,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:17.89,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,I guess bad guys target this \Nschool since it's full of nobles?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:21.95,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm safe on that front, \Nconsidering I'm a commoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:33.85,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.84,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Someoneâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:39.02,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet. I'm not a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:40.79,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:43.53,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,Your name was... Alicia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:48.10,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. Remember, the \Nguy who broke your fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:50.46,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Edwin... Your Highness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:53.77,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there's some stuff going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:55.24,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,"Stuff"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:57.73,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to look into...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:01.25,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,But when I tried to sneak into the \Nschool building, they spotted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:03.29,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you the details, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:04.35,main,TeacherA,0000,0000,0000,,Find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:05.87,main,TeacherB,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see him anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:09.14,main,TeacherA,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Stay on guard, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:10.13,main,TeacherB,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.60,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go out there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:17.26,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let me hide here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.34,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.48,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:31.66,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,I know a gentleman shouldn't just \Ndive into a lady's room, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:34.78,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's fine. This almost \Nfeels like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:39.02,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,I've never talked to a member \Nof the royal family before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:43.46,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same for me. I'm always \Nsurrounded by royalty and nobles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:47.37,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,Are all commoner women as violent as you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:51.67,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be mean! I did that because \NI thought you were a robber!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:55.42,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding. Please don't hit me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:02.68,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I owe you one now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:04.97,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,About what happened tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:07.56,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.80,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:12.74,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,I think the coast is clear now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:14.97,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to trouble \Nyou by staying too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:21.20,main,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,See you at the entrance ceremony \Ntomorrow. Goodnight, Alicia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:24.44,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Prince Edwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:33.73,main,Sword TeacherA,0000,0000,0000,,The new students will now enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:54.94,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:08.01,main,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter, Alicia Ehnleit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:11.48,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,H-How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:13.25,main,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,I... just do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:16.17,main,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, are you feeling ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.90,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:24.51,main,Sword TeacherA,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal Academy Entrance \NCeremony will now commence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:29.51,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,Having the privilege to welcome you \Nfirst-years to our school today
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:32.76,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,gives all of us at the academy \Nthe greatest pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:34.52,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,As you are already aware...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:37.02,flashback,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Yumiella!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:40.82,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,That devil's luck of yours \Nis finally about to run out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.33,flashback,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Alicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:03.84,flashback,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:06.49,flashback,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Sacred light magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:09.85,flashback,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,banish the darkness and grant me strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:28.74,flashback,Edwin,0000,0000,0000,,Alicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:33.64,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&H93C4D4&\3c&HE4FBF9&\pos(155.151,246.168)\fade(200,1)}Edwin
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:33.64,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\pos(185.679,302.216)\fade(200,1)}Well done, Alicia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:38.25,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&H8A76CB&\3c&HE4FBF9&\pos(145.454,230.36)}Alicia
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:38.25,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\pos(214.411,327.365)}Thank you, Prince Edwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.18,flashback,Past Life Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,It's morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:52.33,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,This game is called {\i0}Light Magic and the Hero{\i1},
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:50.60,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\bord4\blur3)\fs25\c&HE881DF&\3c&HF8FAFA&\b1\fnTimes New Roman\move(343.462,320.988,312.216,260.988)}Light Magic and the Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:55.18,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\bord4\blur3)\fs25\c&HE881DF&\3c&HF8FAFA&\b1\fnTimes New Roman\pos(311.498,263.503)}Light Magic and the Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:55.19,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,or {\i0}Light and Hero{\i1} for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:55.19,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fs25\frz22.3\pos(353.042,229.282)\bord3\c&HF5F3FE&\3c&HDEDAFA&}Light {\c&HF7DDDC&\3c&HDEAFA2&}and {\c&HB3C3EB&\3c&H585FC9&}Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:57.53,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,It takes place in a world \Nof swords and magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:59.69,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&H945456&\3c&HE4FBF9&\pos(155.151,246.168)}Oswald
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:59.69,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs15\an7\pos(129.237,310)}Not that I don't sympathize... \NBut rules are rules. Just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:00.62,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,The heroine enrolls in the Royal Academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:03.83,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,where she deepens her relationships \Nwith the conquerable characters
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:04.20,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&H5451A5&\3c&HE4FBF9&\pos(155.151,246.168)}William
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:04.20,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\an7\fs15\pos(128.519,310)}You broke curfew too, right? \NI'll help you in. Give me your hand. C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:06.85,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,as she levels up and, eventually, \Ndefeats the Demon Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:08.70,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&H93C4D4&\3c&HE4FBF9&\pos(155.151,246.168)}Edwin
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:08.70,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\an7\pos(128.575,307.605)\fs15}I suppose I owe you one now. \NAbout what happened tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.85,0:14:08.70,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fairly clichÃ© story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:11.77,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,But after the ending in which \Nthe Demon Lord is defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:11.72,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\pos(264.691,307.964)}The Demon Lord is defeated, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:14.20,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\pos(244.219,310.12)}A hidden boss has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:14.20,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,the hidden boss, the game's \Nstrongest foe, appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:17.97,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,She is Yumiella Dolkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:24.48,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs13\bord0\pos(479.82,102.455)\fade(0,300)}Yumiella...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:19.78,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,the villainess who uses dark magic
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:24.48,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\\fs13\bord0\pos(97.329,204.85)\fade(0,300)}Don't tell me you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:23.27,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,and bullies the heroine, \NAlicia, throughout the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:24.48,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\\fs13\bord0\an7\pos(448.934,270.599)\fade(0,300)}I thought you seemed\N suspicious...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:24.48,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs13\bord0\pos(266.487,323.413)\fade(0,300)}(We have to fight her?!)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:27.01,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,And that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:30.36,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,At age fifteen,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:34.02,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way to enter the \NRoyal Academy in the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:39.23,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnGeorgia\b1\pos(320,115.389)\fs25\blur1\bord2\c&HA200D6&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\fade(600,1)}The Hidden Boss Enters the Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.51,0:14:45.54,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,I was five years old when I regained \Nmy memories from my previous life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:50.57,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,While I was attending college, \NI got hit by a truck
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:52.81,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,and reincarnated in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:58.09,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Some research confirmed \Nthat this was, in fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:02.46,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,the world of {\i0}Light and \NHero{\i1}, the game I played.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:06.25,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Pondering why it happened won't do any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:09.42,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,All I know is that that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:15.20,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,This kingdom was founded by the hero \Nand saint who defeated the Demon Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.72,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Because that Demon Lord was black-haired,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:21.92,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,black hair is seen as unlucky, \Nand even as a symbol of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:29.37,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,That must be one of the things that \Nmakes the villainess what she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:32.17,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Even my servants keep me at arm's length.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:38.18,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I have no memory of ever meeting \Nmy parents, who live in the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:42.33,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Lord can be \Ndefeated at level 70 or so,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:44.31,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,but once Yumiella becomes the hidden boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:46.71,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,one's level has to be \Nmaxed out to defeat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:49.16,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,She is truly the embodiment of unfairness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:52.32,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,But she still gets defeated in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:56.58,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,So does my existence really have any meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:00.82,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:03.78,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,I have the potential to \Nsurpass even the final boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:06.50,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stronger than anyone \Nin the heroine's party,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:10.74,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,and I can use dark magic, which \Nonly enemy characters can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:13.70,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that... actually awesome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:19.55,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! There's no need to recreate the \Nstory of {\i0}Light and Hero{\i1} to the letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.93,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&H5451A5&\3c&HE4FBF9&\pos(155.151,246.168)}William
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.93,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(304.916,333.114)\bord0}Stop picking on Alicia. Don't make me angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:21.98,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&H945456&\3c&HE4FBF9&\pos(155.151,246.168)}Oswald
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:21.98,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\pos(281.212,311.916)}If that's how it must be, I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:23.04,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,I had no interest in the dating \Nsim aspect of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:24.46,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&H93C4D4&\3c&HE4FBF9&\pos(155.151,246.168)}Edwin
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:24.46,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\pos(226.622,306.886)}Stop messing with Alicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:27.34,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,I had no emotional attachment to the \Nthree conquerable characters, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:32.30,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,So instead of living out the \Nstory of {\i0}Light and Hero{\i1},
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:36.30,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,I could just lay low and \Nenjoy a peaceful school life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:40.46,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have nothing to do with \NAlicia or the male leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:45.31,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,That way, I could avoid all risk \Nof becoming the hidden boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:53.26,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&H93C4D4&\3c&HE4FBF9&\pos(155.151,246.168)}Edwin
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:53.26,sign_generic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs17\pos(275.825,304.731)\bord0}Defeat the Demon Lord! Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:47.25,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,and in the spring of our third year,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:50.77,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Alicia and the boys would defeat \Nthe resurrected Demon Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:52.35,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,and we'd all live happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:00.81,flashback italics,Yumiella Age 5,0000,0000,0000,,But I should still raise \Nmy level as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:04.84,flashback italics,Yumiella Age 5,0000,0000,0000,,I need to be strong enough to beat the \NDemon Lord myself if it comes to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:10.63,flashback,Yumiella Age 5,0000,0000,0000,,Yah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:15.13,flashback,Yumiella Age 5,0000,0000,0000,,It comes so naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:20.26,flashback italics,Yumiella Age 5,0000,0000,0000,,When you kill a monster, \Nyou get a magic stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.92,flashback italics,Yumiella Age 5,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to sell these for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:31.11,flashback,Yumiella Age 5,0000,0000,0000,,I think my movements are a little faster now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:33.92,flashback,Yumiella Age 5,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what leveling up feels like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.65,flashback italics,Yumiella Age 5,0000,0000,0000,,The gamer blood in me is boiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:43.36,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,I was always the type to get \Nabsorbed in what I was doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:45.85,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd sneak out of the \Nmansion essentially every day
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:48.41,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,and get engrossed in leveling up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:52.25,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, I made \Nmoney off of magic stones
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:53.80,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,and bought all kinds of items.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:57.45,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,The first thing I bought \Nwas the Amulet of Growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:18:00.74,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,The Amulet of Protection would \Nbe better for keeping me safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:04.95,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,but wearing this would allow \Nme to level up much faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:09.21,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I entered the dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:12.19,flashback italics,Yumiella Age 5,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:15.73,flashback italics,Yumiella Age 5,0000,0000,0000,,I can regenerate an arm \Nwith my magic if I need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:19.83,flashback italics,Yumiella Age 5,0000,0000,0000,,I conquered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:28.13,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,I also acquired the Monster-Calling Flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:32.21,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,And day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:35.34,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,after day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:38.47,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,after day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:47.04,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Until today, at age fifteen,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:50.51,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,I've focused only on leveling up efficiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:53.98,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,I've been through the same dungeon \Nfrom start to end countless times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:02.97,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I'll be able to continue \Nleveling up after I start school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:17.11,main,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Even the building looks just \Nlike it did in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.86,main,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:29.74,italics,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Attend the Royal Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:34.43,italics,Father,0000,0000,0000,,While there, befriend as many sons \Nof high-ranking noblemen as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:39.27,italics,Father,0000,0000,0000,,They don't need to be eldest sons, as I'll \Nhave one marry you and become my heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:44.44,main,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,And this is my first \Ninteraction with my parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:47.04,main,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,I should...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.91,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to lock the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:53.03,main,Oswald,0000,0000,0000,,It's the rule that the Royal \NAcademy's main gate closes at 6 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:56.48,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,But the bell hasn't even finished ringing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.27,0:20:01.55,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,It's really playing out just \Nlike it did in {\i0}Light and Hero{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:05.55,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, the color of your necktie... \NAren't you a first-year, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:08.69,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Avoid getting involved with those four.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:11.61,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,That's the key to having a peaceful life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.99,0:20:17.98,main,Sword TeacherA,0000,0000,0000,,The new students will now enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:22.57,main,Sword TeacherA,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal Academy Entrance \NCeremony will now commence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:27.33,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,Having the privilege to welcome you \Nfirst-years to our school today
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:31.08,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,gives all of us at the academy \Nthe greatest pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:33.06,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,As you are already aware...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:34.08,italicstop,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,I feel eyes on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:37.90,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. It must be my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:41.88,main,Sword TeacherA,0000,0000,0000,,We will now assess your levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:44.25,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,What? Assess our levels?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:51.30,main,Magic Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Alicia Ehnleit: level 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:53.93,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,Work your hardest going forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:55.14,main,Alicia,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.51,0:20:57.58,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,What is my level, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:21:00.31,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I've never checked...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:02.57,main,Magic Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,William Ares: level 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:03.59,main,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:04.78,main,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:06.25,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:09.03,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,They're that excited over level 10?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:13.54,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Then if I don't want to stand out, \NI hope I'm... around level 5?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:16.54,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Level 5...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:20.13,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't be enough to beat a boss character.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:22.95,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Yumiella Dolkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:24.17,main,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.81,0:21:28.55,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,Are you nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:33.31,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. There's nothing embarrassing \Nabout being level 1 when you start school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.93,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not why I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:49.49,main,Magic Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Eldest daughter of Count \NDolkness, Yumiella Dolkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:51.92,main,Magic Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,L-Level 99?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.92,0:21:53.33,main,Students,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:54.50,main,Students,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:56.56,main,StudentA,0000,0000,0000,,Level 99?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:09.14,italics,Yumiella,0000,0000,0000,,Well... goodbye to my peaceful life...
